name: Ivory
description:
This is a re-merge of Butterscotch that is intended to lean a bit more towards anime and produce images with better colors.

Capable of both male and female generations (leans more towards NSFW), though I never really generate many male centered images.

Future version may be implemented to help with hand generation (Hands are usually generated pretty well but not perfect).

No baked VAE in this version.

None of the sample images have used controlnet or been impainted to show how the model truly performs.

All sample images have been generated using Euler a and upscaled with foolhardy_Remacri at denoising strength 0.3.

Additionally the sample images were generated with no VAE being used.
